text: Steve Kaiser is an American politician. He was a member of the Arizona State Senate and Arizona House of Representatives. When he was in the House, he made laws about housing. He resigned from the Senate in June 2023 to focus on his 501(c) organization, The Arizona Prosperity Project. https://ballotpedia.org/Steve_Kaiser https://www.azleg.gov/senate- member/?legislature=56&legislator;=2131 https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/politics/legislature/2023/06/14/republican- sen-steve-kaiser-to-resign-from-legislature/70323075007/?scrlybrkr=e499d722 ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Arizona Legislature Category:Politicians from Arizona Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
